title: location
ev_winter_survival_apr_2019_density_exp: Big Oaks National Wildlife Refuge, Madison, IN, USA

title: plot
ev_winter_survival_apr_2019_density_exp: experimental plot, which corresponds to planting treatment (1 - 10)

title: ID
ev_winter_survival_apr_2019_density_exp: plant ID (A = focal adult, 1 - 3 = focal seedlings, other = background)

title: survival
ev_winter_survival_apr_2019_density_exp: indicator variable of whether plant had green leaves or not
